From: Marcos <marcosbrendonaz@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 18:05:12 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 5/8] feat: combinatorial hardware profiles + fix platform
 consistency
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Replace fixed 24 profiles with combinatorial system:
  39 GPUs × 9 cores × 6 RAM × 5 textures = 10,530+ unique combinations
- All profiles are Windows-only to match Sec-CH-UA-Platform HTTP header
- Remove Mac/Linux profiles that caused platform mismatch detection
- Revert brand spoofing (causes more harm than good)
- Clean up navigator_ua_data.cc unused spoofing code

Achieved Suspect Score 0 on Fingerprint Pro with clean proxy IP.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
